Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win and reach an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Basis104.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down, amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponent is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many people do you have to hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hurt anyone, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have an objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I crush you, my mission's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Croce di Pietro and Roman Church will make the perfect world for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of objective is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking so arrogantly when you're just watching others do the work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do the work for me, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I don't really care who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone just has to group up the various principles and ideas of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to protect that basis no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's your objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get those kind of complicated arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't just give into such a stupid request like handing over Academy City and everyone in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that because you don't know, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never seen someone just stand there in shock at what is occurring in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never heard someone simply say, "It hurts."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, that's no reason to attack Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't justify using someone as a stepping stone for someone else's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:06:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The issues you're having are things that everyone feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone fails, and sometimes they fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you fall, you can just stand back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you look miserable, even if everything doesn't go as planned, you have to stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just throw someone else's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which will you choose, Oriana Thomson?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you failed once, are you going to let others do things for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they failed, are you going to lend those failures a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ending this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I state this to all of the abilities in my body:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unleash your full potential, and destroy the target in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you put even a little effort into making this festival a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is beyond my expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were all trying to protect the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back at your hospital room before the Night Parade starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So wait for me, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the mark of my determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:09:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm just going to let that all go to waste?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me, go for the Croce di Pietro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make Oriana reveal where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it from activating...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will end soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidvia Lorenzetti...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:10:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Croce di Pietro will soon activate, and Academy City will be put under the Roman Catholic Church's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to just get rid of people like us who get in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We grieve over your wounds and wish to heal them as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, only if we can determine that doing so will profit the Roman Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't argue with her, Kamijou Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidvia should be close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cross, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should clarify.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Croce di Pietro is not in Academy City at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At its peak, the area of Roman Catholic Church revival affected by the Croce di Pietro was 47,000 square kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe to assume that it'll easily cover the entirety of Academy City even if it's activated outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oriana was just a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:11:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfortunate that she was defeated, but the Croce di Pietro will turn even that into a beneficial situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only point that is of concern to us now is that science will bow to religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By denying science and showing our power, we will show the power of the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Searching and attacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado can't use magic twice in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not destroy Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we make you throw away the cult of science, we will embrace you as loving comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Tsuchimikado
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have him use his search magic to calculate Lidvia's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I use my communication spell, we can leave it to the forces outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Croce di Pietro will change the world in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,107 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Checkmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some trump card to turn this situation around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A spell used by the constellations in the night sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering starlight on the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many points outside of Academy City are there that can cover all of Academy City?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the furthest point matching those criteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The northern perimeter of Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About 1700 meters out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&Hfef6ed&\fs35\blur1\fax0.1\bord0\shad0\pos(641,167)\frz38.797}Daihaseisai Schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20 more seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, it's the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is the end, then it's over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think so Lidvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I destroyed your illusion, I couldn't even keep the promise I made with my classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The current time is exactly 6:30pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In case you didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when the Night Parade starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this much light, the stars can be blotted out easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost to the light that everyone protecting the Daihaseisai created.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:14:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have figured out who the main character of the Daihaseisai is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally I think you should destroy the Croce di Pietro and promise not to bother Academy City anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have forgotten that I am a devout member of the Roman Catholic Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess you're going to be running around in a game of tag, just like a sports festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidvia Lorenzetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You engaged in a battle that may have determined the fate of Academy City and the world without letting me know,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and on top of that, you got hospitalized after getting beaten up by a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Index-san, whenever I mention magic you always come stumbling right into the middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, that makes it sound like I'm really stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you never noticed shows that you're a real—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My my, what a delightful scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having a serious talk here, so get out, short hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinary citizens are allowed to cooperate in Judgment's peacekeeping, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama, you do realize this is a hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see today's final results?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our school sailed right past yours into first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you haven't forgotten about our agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I can't do anything like that with my body in this condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Oriana Thompson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all those poor lost sinners. {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem, attention please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Archbishop of the Church of England, Laura Stewart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now that I've introduced myself, you can't ignore me right, Lidvia Ojou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find me in this private jet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had them slap on a little present onto the wall of your plane at Haneda.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite creepy, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That personality of yours where you laugh harder the more you're pressured...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything you can do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The harsher the pain, the sweeter the joy will be upon overcoming it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must give thanks to the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The taller a wall is, the greater the satisfaction upon getting over it, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is some truth in what you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you little animal at the edge of a cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidvia, I don't mind saving you if you give up on Rome's teachings and lick my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe you and that thing can make a crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Croce di Pietro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:17:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow that to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this speed of descent I should make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I definitely will make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's what makes it fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Lidvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which will you pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most powerful spiritual tool in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or the lost and pitiful servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The greater the challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the greater the satisfaction once you trample over me, the creator of the challenge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will trample...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,over that unreachable flower...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as much as I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite the tremor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The development of the key, Imagine Breaker, is still unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have to consider the possibility of taking action myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sleeping on the bench in the waiting room,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they told me I can't use it in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bed is so nice and soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The frog doctor said I can leave tomorrow or the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look kind of sad, Aisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he go do something reckless again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, I haven't heard all the details yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently the Roman Catholic magicians tried to take advantage of the Daihaseisai to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, without saying a single word to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he went on a huge rampage and only told me about it like he was making a report after it all happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter who it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll help out anyone in need...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't have been saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like all I do is cause trouble for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma seems to enjoy spending time with you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.39,0:21:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Fukiyose-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind hospital visit is this, suddenly slapping me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone would be surprised with seeing a naked boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who barged in while I was in the middle of changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I asked him, he said it was for his own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's what happiness is for Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For better or for worse, Index and I suddenly find ourselves headed for Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we might as well relax and look at the sights!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is that Orsola?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Amakusa Church too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: "City of Water."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross, the story begins.
